#CircuitBreakerSG D-38

Finally acceded to their requests to make Cereal something. With extra cereal they said... Oh sure! Crispy Cereal with tender Chicken thigh who wouldn't like?

Next dish is Cabbage with Gluten Puff & Chickpeas & lastly air-fried Otah.

Enjoy your #dinner too!

#sghomecook #sghomecooking #sgfood #sgfoodies #sgeats #singaporehomecooks #simplecooking #igsg #igfoodies #whati8today #instafood_sg #singaporefood #CircuitBreaker #cookingathome #eatathome #stayhome #stayhomeandcook #sgunited #CircuitBreakerCookingChallenge #StayHomeWithAscott
#stayhomeforSG #ImStayingHome #cerealchicken #chicken #otah
@happycathgoh Thanks so much, Kath! Love your cooking & baking too 👍
Looks so tempting, always love to virtual eat your dishes😄😂
@tamjiak_veggiez Yes, dear. You can try cereal tofu 👍
I love cereal anything! 😍 prawns, chicken or anything!
@make.happyy wow... why does it sound sinfully delicious 😋
@yvonnemsw Cos' we sin big or go home. Your Cereal Chicken is calling me though !
'Zhi-char' game-strong ! I like mine, very sinfully with prawns, salted egg-yolk and curry leaf.
@t.elyn_elyn.t Not a tiny piece of cereal was leftover 😆
Very addictive and tasty. I don’t think there will be any leftovers Yvonne 😋😋
That cereal chicken is so perfect 😍
Yummy with chicken too 😍 I cooked extra bowl of cereal for my kids too
@floatsam_and_jetsam There's cereal anything other than prawns; tofu, sotong, pork, chicken, etc 😅
@tet_chu Try it, try it. Let me know if you like it 👌
Me me! I’ve never cooked this dish... shall try! Cereal chicken
@yvonnemsw I dowan to be too greedy maaaaah!!!!
Extra cereal for mine too pls!!! I'll just need 5 pcs of the chicken. Deliver to my place tom ok? 🤣🤣🤣🤣
That cereal chicken is definetely a Dang!!! 👍🏼
@easy_busy_kitchen Anything will cereal will be a hit 😋
Such a great idea to make crispy chicken with cereal👍👍😋
Crispy chicken I mean cereal chicken😋Love everything on the table😍
Wow, I never hear off cereal chicken. Interesting idea. Love it! 👍
@vnm_lee Thanks so much for your kind words 😍
This looks like what I order in the restaurant, so legit n so yummy!! 😋
